Requirements:
CentOS 7+
Git
Vim-enhanced
----------------------------------
Install git and vim-enhanced packages on the linux box.
#yum install -y git vim-enhanced

Configure git:
#git config --global user.name "Amit Prajapati"
#git config --global user.email "xxx"

Set ~/.bashrc and ~/.vimrc for better scripting and programming in Developement env. 
Reference: https://github.com/linuxacademy/content-python-for-sys-admins
